<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<style>
    body {
        background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498721181593-8be06ae6e5a6?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&ixid=MnwzNjYxOXwwfDF8c2VhY3J8MXx8fGVkdWNhdGlvbnxlbnwwfHx8fDE2Nzk2MjI1NzA&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&w=1080') no-repeat center center fixed;
        background-size: cover;
        animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; }
        to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    .overlay {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 3rem;
        z-index: 10;
    }

    .content h2 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .point {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .point h3 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .point p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    }
</style>

<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen relative">
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>

        <div class="point">
            <h3>1. Empowering Lifelong Learning</h3>
            <p>We envision a world where education is lifelong, continuous, and accessible to all. Our goal is to provide personalized learning experiences that allow learners to expand their knowledge and skillset at any stage in their life, regardless of their location.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
            <h3>2. Democratizing Education</h3>
            <p>Our mission is to break down barriers to education. By leveraging cutting-edge technology, we aim to provide equal access to world-class educational resources, enabling individuals to learn, grow, and succeed on their own terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
            <h3>3. Building a Global Learning Community</h3>
            <p>Education should be a collaborative and inclusive experience. We strive to create a global network of learners and educators, where diverse ideas are shared, innovation is encouraged, and everyone has the opportunity to contribute to collective progress.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
